Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.19,0:00:04.55,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,An inactive virus vaccine isn't feasible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:07.48,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,And I'm not getting anywhere \Nwith a weakened variant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:08.23,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:12.74,Flashback,Gu,0,0,0,,Give me one month.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:16.73,Italics,Gu,0,0,0,,Do I need to keep that promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:22.87,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Experiments on living creatures \Nare difficult, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:25.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.47,0:00:28.25,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! I was thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.25,0:00:29.83,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,I'm fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.83,0:00:33.26,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,A m-m-m-man!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:36.76,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:43.20,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,My signature?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.20,0:00:44.02,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:45.59,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.59,0:00:46.52,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:50.90,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,He's a pervert who attacks any woman he sees.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:53.06,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,B-Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:55.53,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Pervert?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:57.28,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,That's rather rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:00:59.95,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You pinned a woman to the ground in \Nthe hallway back there, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:01.41,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,No! She...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:02.91,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:07.92,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You won't be getting all this attention \Njust because you're a man for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:09.51,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:15.30,Italics,Gi,0,0,0,,Mizuhara-sama, can we speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:16.68,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Suou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:19.54,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,What do you mean you're not going \Nto be my attendant anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:20.72,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Mizuhara-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:22.22,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.57,0:01:24.04,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Good, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:25.23,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:30.51,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,This is Katagiri Rea and Kuroda Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.51,0:01:32.73,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Your new attendants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:08.33,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:12.53,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Mizuhara Reito, you are \Nnow famous worldwide,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:15.61,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,and in a unique position compared \Nto the rest of the Numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:18.88,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Thus, we're giving you \Nmore than one attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:22.09,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,There's no rule saying you can only have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:24.95,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Kuroda Maria is a researcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:27.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Our technology director \Ntrusts her quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.32,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,She'll be useful in your research.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:32.60,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,N-Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:37.41,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Katagiri will relieve Suou \Nand see to your needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:40.54,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,She was a Citizen Relations Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:41.49,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Citizen Relations Officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:46.70,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Her job was to interact with the people \Non behalf of UW, and keep them pacified.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.84,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,She knows the outside world well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:51.34,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,If you want to know something, ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:55.08,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I'll be going, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:03:59.09,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Suou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:03.97,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Why did you make her leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:08.93,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,If you like her that much, \Njust mate with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:09.89,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,I will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:12.18,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Don't get so mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:17.33,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,As soon as the paperwork is finished, \NSuou Mira will no longer be your attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:20.82,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,But she may still stay with \Nyou as a mating candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:28.28,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,It's your fault she was forced to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:34.64,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Her most important mission was to get you \Nto mate with as many girls as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:38.84,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,She failed, so of course she lost the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:42.19,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,If you don't like it, then why \Nnot go mate with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:47.64,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,And while I'll permit you to \Ncontinue your research into a cure,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:53.35,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,if you're not going to mate with anyone, \Nyour other freedoms will be restricted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:55.23,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:00.22,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Mira!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:02.58,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:03.61,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:05.59,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You've lost weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:09.12,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Take care of Mizuhara-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:13.26,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry about that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:16.87,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,He's just a loser who only \Nthinks of women as tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:20.88,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,That's not who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:22.44,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:23.88,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Wait! Listen, Mira!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.86,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,If you let your guard down around a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:31.22,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You're as beautiful as ever, aren't you? \NLike time's stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:38.40,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Um, Kuroda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:40.00,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Y-Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:42.95,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,What is there where we're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:45.86,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,It's called Keimon City. \NThere is a hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:48.16,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,A hot spring? Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:52.62,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Um... somebody important in \Nthe MK Virus research field.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:54.12,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Somebody important?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.36,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:58.62,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.61,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I'll go change.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:08.26,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You should just go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:13.35,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I'm not Mizuhara-san's attendant right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:17.78,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You've got a difficult \Npersonality, too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:25.86,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kuroda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:28.36,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,No, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:31.44,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I'm not used to men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:33.53,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Is it okay if we try to \Nbe a little more casual?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:35.12,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,We're close, age-wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:37.51,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:41.55,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Kuroda-san, you said you \Nstudy virology, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:42.63,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:47.13,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I know a decent amount about \Nthe MK Virus, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:49.88,Flashback_Italics,Gi,0,0,0,,The MK Virus was artificially created!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:54.16,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,How do you think it was born?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:56.73,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,There are three theories \Non the origin of viruses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:57.93,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,The regressive hypothesis,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:01.89,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,The escape hypothesis, \Nand the virus-first hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.89,0:07:03.93,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,But we don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:08.28,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,And since we don't know, "how it was born" \Nmay not even be the right phrase to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:14.40,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,It's possible that something that's existed for \Neons only just now came in contact with humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:19.54,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,In fact, in biology, viruses aren't \Neven treated as living creatures...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:21.53,Italics,Gu,0,0,0,,She's suddenly much more talkative...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:25.29,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Is it possible that a human made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:28.91,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,You've got an interesting theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:31.06,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Put on your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:35.55,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,We might find some clues where we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:37.85,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:43.94,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Keimon City is where the first victim \Nof the MK Virus in Japan appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.71,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:51.07,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,The lake's so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:55.23,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,There's a group of students on a trip here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:56.58,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,But beyond that, we have \Nthe place to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.92,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I heard we're having \Nspiny lobster for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:00.97,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Let's go play ping-pong! Ping-pong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:02.71,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Forget that. Let's hit the hot springs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:05.29,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,We're not here to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:07.54,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,This place is pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:10.55,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I wish Mahiru-chan could've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:13.68,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,We can't let an outsider tag along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:17.80,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Creating an environment that relaxes \NReito is part of your job, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:21.36,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,My job is to manage his daily life
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:24.06,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,and help him focus on viral research.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:26.44,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,We disagree there, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:28.19,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:33.98,Main,GI,0,0,0,,That looks fun! Let me join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:36.53,Main,GI,0,0,0,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:42.61,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,I wish I could've gone into \Nthe open-air bath, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.58,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,A holographic open-air bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:50.84,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,This isn't bad either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:57.86,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:09:01.76,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,It's fine. It's more fun \Nif we all go in together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:04.98,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,There's no "Men's Bath" and \N"Women's Bath" these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:07.32,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,I'll leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:08.23,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:11.86,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I'll wash your back as thanks \Nfor all the help you give me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:15.09,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,No, you're the one who's \Nhelping me all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.62,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,It's the other way around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.37,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Then maybe I'll ask you for help, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:23.78,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Wash our backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:31.28,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,It's so nice, having Reito-sama wash my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:33.95,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Okay, all clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:35.51,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.99,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,G-Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.79,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:44.20,Italics,Gi,0,0,0,,She's like a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:47.20,Italics,Gi,0,0,0,,Does her personality change when \Nshe's talking about the virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:51.90,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Sorry! Was it too hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:54.28,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I'll do the rest myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:57.32,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.28,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:09.04,Italics,Gu,0,0,0,,She has such a pretty back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:11.13,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Why not have him wash yours, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:12.51,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:14.80,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm last, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:17.57,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,It's finally over...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:19.09,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:23.60,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,My skin is sensitive. \NWill you wash me with your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:30.85,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,That feels so good. You're good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:33.11,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,I-I'll wash it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:36.36,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Not yet. Here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:42.37,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You can do the legs, too, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:46.87,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Run your hands over every little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.48,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,And lastly this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:54.48,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:56.63,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Do the rest yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:59.19,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,And I was so close, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:05.64,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,It's been so long since \NI've seen Ms. Taniguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:09.14,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I'm Katagiri Rea with UW's Japan branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:09.89,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:11.18,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:15.51,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,We're here to talk about your husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:18.65,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I told you everything I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.23,0:11:21.27,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I saw your press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.41,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:25.21,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,But it's not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:29.41,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,My husband's not coming back, \Neven if you do make a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:33.31,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Taniguchi-san, can you \Ntell us what your husband
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:37.34,Main,,0,0,0,,was doing just before \Nhe contracted the virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.05,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:40.80,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Please! This is for all humanity's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:43.68,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You took his body and sliced it into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:48.21,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Ma'am, that's called an autopsy. We have \Nto do it to find out what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:49.72,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:52.56,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,He hated doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:54.23,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Taniguchi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.56,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:58.32,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,What do I have to do to get you to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:02.04,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You can screw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:04.82,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I'm joking, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.26,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:14.50,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,The MK Virus appeared in multiple \Nspots all around the world at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:17.41,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,There's a theory that it was bioterrorism \Nby a nation-state or terrorist group.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:18.77,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,A theory it arose naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:22.76,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,And even a theory that the Earth \Nitself created it to purge humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:25.68,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,But we don't know where it came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:31.64,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Ms. Taniguchi's husband was \Nthe first victim in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:37.02,Episode_Number,Gi,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}Episode 5
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.48,0:12:37.02,Episode_Title,Gi,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}First Victim
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.61,0:12:36.52,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,He hated technology and had no GPS on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:39.89,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,If we knew what he was doing and where he was
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:43.29,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,before he got sick, \Nit might give us a clue, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:47.00,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,She greatly distrusts UW.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:50.17,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,The government at the time was really rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.49,0:12:57.29,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,The person you care about was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:01.82,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Why not meet him, Erisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.72,Sign_Basic,,0,0,0,,{\fs12\c&HBCA590&\bord2\shad0\b1\an5\frx16\fry354\fay-.17\fax.05\pos(220,147.5)\3c&HECF8F2&}Keimon City Central Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.72,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You never learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.69,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how many times \Nyou come. It won't change a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:08.72,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:13.85,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,If we know what your husband was doing, \Nwe might know where the virus came from!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:17.98,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You should just stop making \Nvaccines and start making kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:22.73,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Your biggest job right now is making kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:26.36,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're having some fun with \Nthe crowd of girls behind you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:27.91,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:34.75,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Mizuhara hasn't mated, that is, had any \Nsexual relations with women after waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:38.88,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,The rest of you, leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.63,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:47.68,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Most people in your situation would be going \Nat it like a rabbit with any girl he could find.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:51.14,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You'd have enough time left \Nover to research the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:53.49,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,I don't have the kind of \Npersonality you'd need
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:56.77,Main,,0,0,0,,to be having fun with girls \Nwhile doing research.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:58.68,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You gay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:00.21,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:02.25,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,There are a lot of girls who are very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:05.40,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,And honestly, I'd love to \Ndo what they want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.87,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:09.24,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,That's what would benefit the world the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:13.53,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,There's a girl I'm in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.99,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,I know it's selfish,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:22.25,Main,,0,0,0,,but I figured if I put my efforts into \Nfinding a cure for the MK Virus,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:25.76,Main,,0,0,0,,it would make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:30.30,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,We're done talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:44.40,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,It feels so good to be outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:49.53,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,If Rea-san finds out I brought you to the \Nopen-air bath, she'll get mad at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:52.22,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,It's fine! Nobody's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:55.16,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Don't blame me if something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:58.42,Italics,Gu,0,0,0,,Taniguchi-san managed to \Navoid telling me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:14:59.53,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.53,0:15:01.17,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Reito-sama, hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:05.05,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Um, this bath is in use...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:06.24,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:07.69,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,The students?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:11.61,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,I'll just have to hide in here for a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:15.56,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:18.22,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:23.82,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,I'll be going—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:25.86,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Leave, and I'll scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:30.49,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,If you don't want to \Ncause a ruckus, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:33.24,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Why are you wearing a yukata in the sauna?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:37.27,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Because I'm an exchange \Nstudent that loves Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:40.06,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,The rich depths of the Japanese heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.50,Italics,Gu,0,0,0,,I don't think that's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:44.75,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Now, let's play a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:51.63,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,If I leave the sauna first, \NI won't tell anybody you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:53.39,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,And if I leave first...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:59.89,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You'll have to do one thing I tell \Nyou to do, Mizuhara Reito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:02.77,Italics,Gu,0,0,0,,She knows me. Of course she would.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:05.68,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Let's see who can last longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:13.78,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,It's so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:15.69,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I should introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:20.29,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I'm Chloe. I'm an exchange \Nstudent from America.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:23.23,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Y-Your Japanese is very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:25.29,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,A little weird, but good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:28.80,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I love Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:32.05,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Would you like to have sex with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:35.93,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Oh, you call it "mating," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:39.68,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You shouldn't try to endure \Nthings for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:44.19,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,That goes for the sauna, \Nand for a woman's temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.72,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,I'm good at self-control.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:50.57,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,What about you? You should \Nprobably give up and leave soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:59.20,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Your samurai soul is impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:05.70,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Have some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:09.49,Italics,Gu,0,0,0,,I should call Akane-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:10.71,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:14.72,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Feed me with your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.01,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:17.84,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,I'll go get the nurse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:21.60,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,If you don't... I'll scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:29.11,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Reito-sama, I brought help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:36.11,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Reito-sama is mating with a \Nstrange woman before any of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.49,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,No, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.62,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Reito-sama, you traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:41.57,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Sorry for bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:41.57,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You're such an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:43.37,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,You've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:45.32,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,That was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:47.37,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,It was an act?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:50.25,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,American girls are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:53.15,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,It'd take more than that to knock me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:58.78,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Now let's have a nice long \Nchat, Mizuhara Reito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:03.44,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:04.43,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:05.86,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:06.94,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:10.69,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,There's a bakery on the corner \Njust outside this building, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:12.94,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I want a white bean jam pastry from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:15.40,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I can send someone from UW...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:18.69,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I'm not eating it unless he gets it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:20.59,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,All right. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:21.45,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Mizuhara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:25.71,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:28.92,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I want to talk with you privately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.21,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:34.84,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You know about Tachibana Erisa, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:38.47,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,She's Mizuhara-sama's childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.84,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:50.14,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I'll ask a different question, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:53.33,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Tell me what that kid's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:55.68,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Why do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:57.11,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Just answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:59.86,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Don't you want to help him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:03.87,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Mizuhara-sama is very selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:08.43,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,It's wonderful that he's working on a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:13.34,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,But I think he could mate at least once or \Ntwice a week even while doing his research.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:15.66,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,With the world on the brink of destruction,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:20.23,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,having someone he's in love with is not \Na good enough reason to refuse mating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:24.14,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,He really is selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:28.14,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,But not many people could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:31.99,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,He has the same desires as any normal man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:33.65,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,But he's always fighting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:38.34,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,And he can keep being selfish \Nin the face of the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:41.91,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,He may really be able to save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:45.41,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You know him well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:48.68,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Well, I'm always watching him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:51.92,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:52.97,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:54.17,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I don't want it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:58.55,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Are you never going to have kids, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:03.56,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,If it really will help humanity, \NI might, some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:07.68,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You'll give up on the girl you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:12.95,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,No. Even if I did mate, I'd only \Ndo it because they wanted me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.95,0:20:14.69,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,My heart wouldn't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:18.19,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,I only love one girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:22.55,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I'm tired today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:24.42,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,Come back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:27.61,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I'll make you listen to \Nme talk about old times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.61,0:20:28.45,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:31.58,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,I would like to talk about \Nmy husband once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:34.46,Main,Gu,0,0,0,,I'll come! I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:43.97,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,No one would fault you for giving up on saving \Nthe world and being with the man you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:47.87,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You're so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:50.85,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry, you'll lose him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:53.13,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,He had a whole bunch of pretty \Nladies with him today—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:56.36,Italics,Gi,0,0,0,,Even if Reito falls in \Nlove with someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:59.08,Italics,Gi,0,0,0,,I'll only ever love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:05.61,Main,Gi,0,0,0,,You're both very similar.
